# K8s Manifests Conventions

## CloudNativePG Cluster

```yaml
apiVersion: postgresql.cnpg.io/v1
kind: Cluster
metadata:
  name: pg-{app}
  namespace: puchi-db
spec:
  instances: 1
  imageName: ghcr.io/cloudnative-pg/postgresql:18.0
  storage:
    size: 10Gi
    storageClass: local-path
  bootstrap:
    initdb:
      database: {db_name}
      owner: {username}
      secret:
        name: pg-{app}-secret
```

## Backend Deployment

Mỗi service có:
- ConfigMap: `{service}-config` chứa config.yaml (server, data, auth)
- Deployment: image `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-{service}:latest`
- Service: `{service}-service` (ClusterIP)
- Ports: HTTP **8000** (auth + các service khác), gRPC **9000** (các service Kratos; auth không có gRPC)

Auth config trong ConfigMap (các Go service):
```yaml
auth:
  auth_service_url: "http://auth-service.puchi-backend.svc.cluster.local:8000"
  public_paths:
    - /v1/health
    - /v1/healthz
```

## Frontend Deployment

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: web
  namespace: puchi-frontend
spec:
  containers:
    - env:
      - name: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL
        value: "https://puchi.io.vn"
      - name: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
        value: "https://api.puchi.io.vn"
```

## Envoy Gateway

### GatewayClass → Gateway
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: GatewayClass  # name: envoy-gateway
kind: Gateway       # name: puchi-gateway, listener HTTP:80
```

### SecurityPolicy (CORS only — NO extAuth)
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.envoyproxy.io/v1alpha1
kind: SecurityPolicy
spec:
  targetRefs:
    - group: gateway.networking.k8s.io
      kind: HTTPRoute
      name: puchi-api-routes
  cors:
    allowOrigins: ["https://puchi.io.vn", "http://localhost:3000"]
    allowCredentials: true
```
Session introspect do từng Go backend service tự xử lý qua `pkg/auth/` (extAuth không cấu hình ở Envoy).

### HTTPRoute
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: HTTPRoute
spec:
  parentRefs:
    - name: puchi-gateway
  rules:
    - matches:
        - path:
            type: PathPrefix
            value: /auth
      backendRefs:
        - name: auth-service
          namespace: puchi-backend
          port: 8000
    - matches:
        - path:
            type: PathPrefix
            value: /core
      backendRefs:
        - name: core-service
          namespace: puchi-backend
          port: 8000
```

## Auth-service Deployment (Limen)

File: `infra/backend/auth/deployment.yaml`

- ConfigMap: auth-config (limen base_url, trusted_origins, cookie_domain, db, nats)
- Secrets (cluster-managed, **không** commit giá trị vào git):
  - `auth-limen-secret` → `LIMEN_SECRET` (32 bytes)
  - `auth-oauth-credentials` → `GOOGLE_*`, `FACEBOOK_*`, `TIKTOK_*`
- Service: auth-service (ClusterIP:**8000**)
- OAuth callbacks: `https://api.puchi.io.vn/auth/oauth/{google|facebook|tiktok}/callback`
## Garage buckets

```bash
curl -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"globalAlias":"puchi-{bucket}"}' \
  http://{garage}:3903/v2/CreateBucket
```

## NATS streams

```bash
nats str add puchi-{name} \
  --subjects "puchi.{domain}.>" \
  --storage file \
  --max-bytes=1GB
```
